						               													<description>Heart of the City is very special addition to the game bringing an 84mm miniature as well as additional 50 stories and 5 cards. This huge, destroyed monument will symbolize &amp;ldquo;heart&amp;rdquo; of the destroyed city, where people tend to gather and where you never know what to expect.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mechanically, this will be a whole new location that you will be able to visit. After scavenging we will decide ourselves if we want to visit the center of the city additionally or if it's too risky, BUT you will never know what to expect there. It will not be just one-time additional exploration &amp;ndash; in this area some of the most intense things will be happening. It can be either positive or negative, you will never know until you will decide to go there. The system will of course possess an inner balancing mechanic so there is no chance for a &amp;quot;festival of randomness&amp;quot; and drawing 4 of the worst cards or the other way around. Heart of the city will also consist of special stories for that region and we will make sure they will be very, very memorable.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;'&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
